# Week 5 – Neural Networks for Vision Tasks

Dataset: **CIFAR-10** (auto-downloaded on first run)

## Setup
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Run each step
```bash
python image_captioning.py       # Step 3 – RNN captioning  → output_captioning.png
python attention_captioning.py   # Step 4 – Attention captions → output_attention_captions.png
python image_gradients.py        # Step 5 – Saliency + confusion matrix → output_saliency.png, output_confusion_matrix.png
python style_transfer.py         # Step 6 – Style transfer → output_style_transfer.png
```

## Output files
| File | Used for |
|---|---|
| `output_captioning.png` | RNN caption on one image |
| `output_attention_captions.png` | ViT+GPT-2 captions, all 10 classes |
| `output_saliency.png` | Saliency heatmaps, all 10 classes |
| `output_training_curves.png` | Loss & accuracy curves over epochs |
| `output_perclass_accuracy.png` | Per-class accuracy bar chart |
| `output_tsne.png` | t-SNE feature embedding scatter plot |
| `output_style_transfer.png` | Style transfer before/after |